  "title": "Deliciously Dense French Cheese Gratin",
  "description": "A rich and flavorful dish from Brittany, featuring a blend of herbal notes and a satisfying cheese pull, made with a mirepoix base and whole30 friendly ingredients. This gratin is perfect for a special occasion or a cozy night in.",
